<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Incident Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Incident Report for Guard <%= content.guardName %></h2>
    <p>Dear <%= content.ownerName %>,</p>
    <p>I am writing to inform you of an incident that I observed while on duty as Guard <%= content.guardName %> at site <%= content.siteName %></p>
    <h3>Incident Details:</h3>
    <p><%= content.comment %></p>

    <h3>Incident Images:</h3>
    <ul>
        <% for (let i = 0; i < content.images.length; i++) { %>
            <li><img src="../uploads/"<%= content.images[i] %>" alt="Incident Image" style="max-width: 100%;"></li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>
    <p>If you need more information or if there are further steps to be taken, please contact me at <%= content.guardContact %>.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The Guard Management Team</p>
</body>
</html>
